getbac.sh :
run as ./getbasc.sh
used to download the input to files. name all the files to download in the for loop and it will download the data in same files.

makefasta.sh:
run as ./makefasta.sh c1 c2
This file splits the file mentioned in the for loop after c1 whenever it identified c1.c2 and creater a fasta file.
It assumes that the files are in input folder
